race.description: Bet365 New Racing App Mdn Plate
race.comment: POLYMER (4) debuts for the McEvoys and has impressed at the jumpouts. Harry Coffey sticks from the last two and he maps well. Left the one to beat. JURA VAUDOIS (7) resumed improved when narrowly beaten at Mildura. She has the rail and is free running. Fitter again and is sure to give a sight. THE BIRTHDAY PARTY (10) debuts and has jumped out six times since February. She won the latest at Flemington and has an inside barrier with a 2kg claimer aboard. Has to be kept very safe. VINNIE'S TURN (6) resumes and has shown enough to keep onside. Placed in a recent Seymour jumpout and will be naturally improved.
